low defensive penalty<br>
effect: nine second stun<br>
<br>
<br>
the above style set gives you tons of options.  no bleed so you dont break mez.  only overpowered stun is a followup to back positional, hibs get this with just straight back positional.  freedom from the tyrrany of no hit bonus &quot;styles&quot;, if you would call the insult that is them a style.  i think this would really help us as a class.  it's really tough to overpower a style set with reactionaries and positionals, and if you look above there's no doublefrost equivalent in sight.  also the majority of these styles are medium or high endurance use so a solo skald would be going oop in short order.<br>
<br>
i have tried REALLY HARD to make a *good* style set, but not a *too good* style set.<br>
<br>
